@startuml
title CollabMD workspace handoff

actor Author
actor Reviewer
participant "Vault on Disk" as Vault
participant "CollabMD" as App

Author -> App : open workspace
Reviewer -> App : join the same room
App -> Vault : load files
Author -> App : edit showcase.md
App --> Reviewer : sync changes in realtime
Reviewer -> App : open backlink / outline context
Reviewer -> App : add anchored comment
App --> Author : show thread marker and preview bubble
Author -> App : resolve feedback
App -> Vault : persist final text
@enduml
